headline: Cadence Design Systems’s Q3 Earnings Call: Our Top 5 Analyst Questions
summary: Cadence Design Systems’ third quarter results surpassed Wall Street’s expectations for both revenue and non-GAAP earnings per share, yet the market responded with a modestly negative reaction. Management attributed the solid performance to broad-based demand across electronic design automation (EDA), intellectual property (IP), and hardware platforms, particularly as AI-driven design activity accelerated across multiple industries. CEO Anirudh Devgan highlighted strong bookings and a record back
